I should add my 2 cents here. I am experiencing pretty much the same issue, although my error message is a little different.

WARNING:tensorflow:IOError [Errno 2] No such file or directory: '/usr/local/lib/python2.7/site-packages/tensorflow/tensorboard/TAG' on path /usr/local/lib/python2.7/site-packages/tensorflow/tensorboard/TAG WARNING:tensorflow:Unable to read TensorBoard tag

In fact, that TAG directory/file is indeed not present on my filesystem.
